{"tid":2487465,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"紐交所推出“第一筆交易”NFT，以紀念Spotify等在公開市場的首次交易","createTime":"2021-04-13T14:23:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T14:41:08.000Z","uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a2dcb5871e64d9f345a258896801d5cd1c5b0bb3","tid":2487465,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:23:08.000Z","msg":"據報導，紐約證券交易所周一宣布，將推出&ldquo;第一筆交易&rdquo;(First Trade) NFT，以紀念Spotify(<a href=\"http://SPOT.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FSPOT.US&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=4b8db0e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">SPOT.US</a>)<br />\nSnowflake(<a href=\"http://SNOW.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FSNOW.US&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=e3729791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">SNOW.US</a>)<br />\nUnity(<a href=\"http://U.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FU.US&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=cbc804dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">U.US</a>)<br />\nDoorDash(DASH .US)<br />\nRoblox(<a href=\"http://RBLX.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FRBLX.US&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=773101a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">RBLX.US</a>)<br />\nCoupang(<a href=\"http://CPNG.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FCPNG.US&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=e8d2e0e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">CPNG.US</a>)這六隻股票在公開市場上真實的第一筆交易。<br />\n<br />\n紐約證券交易所總裁Stacey Cunningham表示，在一家公司公開上市的時候，交易所在最繁忙的日子里處理超過3500億的訂單、報價和交易信息。每條信息都被記錄在交易所的數字賬本上。<br />\n<br />\nCunningham稱，這些信息中只有一條標誌公司在紐交所的第一筆交易，那就是公司上市的確切時刻。 &ldquo;紐交所First Trade NFT是為了紀念公司歷史上這一獨特時刻。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nNFT(非同質化代幣)是一種使用區塊鏈技術來跟踪虛擬物品所有權的數字資產。今年，隨著比特幣和以太幣等數字貨幣的升值，NFT迅速流行起來。<br />\n<br />\n這個市場正在快速發展，一些數字收藏品的售價高達數百萬美元。 Twitter首席執行官Jack Dorsey以290萬美元的價格售出了第一條推文。與此同時，佳士得拍賣行對藝術家Beeple的一件虛擬作品進行了拍賣，最終以6900萬美元的價格售出。"},{"pid":"6ca53b75849fd31163389ef97a323c81d4bae308","tid":2487465,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:37:45.000Z","msg":"其實即係買咗啲咩？"},{"pid":"ba19ba59b7af422ea9ca958689fafb34c8941bc2","tid":2487465,"uid":2106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ca53b75849fd31163389ef97a323c81d4bae308","tid":2487465,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:37:45.000Z","msg":"其實即係買咗啲咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:41:08.000Z","msg":"一個zip file"}]}